 And it&#39;s the same with anything from Google. I don&#39;t trust them to keep any service besides Search, ads, Analytics, Gmail, and Sheets. Even Android I wouldn&#39;t be shocked if they end up saying &#34;everyone on Fuchsia now!&#34;
